<p>I've read the docs, watched the WWDC video and puzzled over it for a good while. And thought I understood it a few times.</p>  <p>But in reality, it does nothing like what it's suggested it does, and I've been unable to create a scene where it responds in any way predictably.</p>  <p>It could be broken. I suppose. But it's more likely my understanding of what it does is broken.</p>